com.worldpay.library.domain

Class ExtendedInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.worldpay.library.domain.ExtendedInformation

  • public class ExtendedInformation
extends java.lang.Object
    This object contains extended information that is, in general, optional when making a payment request. This will automatically be added to a payment request if not provided so that some terminal information can be passed up to the server (terminal id, if not provided then the terminal serial number will be used, and other information).
